sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant FE as Miniapp
    participant Lido as lido-service
    participant Swap as liquid-swap-service
    participant Wallet as Connected Wallet
    participant ETH as Ethereum

    Note over FE,Lido: JWT already obtained from auth-service

    alt Stake via Protocol (Lido mint)
        FE->>Lido: POST /api/lido/stake { userAddress, amountWei }
        Lido-->>FE: StakingTransaction { transactionData, chainId:1 }
        FE->>Wallet: sendTransaction(transactionData)
        Wallet-->>FE: txHash
        FE->>Lido: POST /api/lido/transaction/submit (optional)
        FE->>ETH: wait/poll receipt(txHash)
        ETH-->>FE: confirmed | reverted | timeout
        FE->>Lido: GET /api/lido/position/:address
    else Unstake via Protocol (queue)
        FE->>Lido: POST /api/lido/unstake { userAddress, amountWei }
        Lido-->>FE: tx type = unstake_approval OR unstake
        alt Approval required
            FE->>Wallet: send approval tx
            Wallet-->>FE: approval txHash
            FE->>ETH: wait receipt
            FE->>Lido: POST /api/lido/unstake again
            Lido-->>FE: tx type = unstake (requestWithdrawals)
        end
        FE->>Wallet: send unstake request tx
        Wallet-->>FE: unstake txHash
        FE->>ETH: wait/poll receipt
        ETH-->>FE: confirmed | reverted | timeout
        Note over FE,Lido: Claim path: POST /api/lido/withdrawals/claim after finalization
    else Stake/Unstake via Market
        FE->>Swap: POST /swap/quote { amount, unit }
        Swap-->>FE: quote
        FE->>Swap: POST /swap/tx { amountWei, sender, route }
        Swap-->>FE: prepared bundle [approval?, swap]
        loop for each tx in bundle
            FE->>Wallet: sendTransaction(tx)
            Wallet-->>FE: txHash
            FE->>ETH: wait/poll receipt
            ETH-->>FE: confirmed | reverted | timeout
        end
        FE->>Lido: refresh position/withdrawals (UI sync)
    end

